ED_Title: Report of the International Residual Mechanism for Criminal Tribunals
ED_DecisionText: At its 19th plenary meeting, on 23 October 2019, the General Assembly took note of the seventh annual report of the International Residual Mechanism for Criminal Tribunals.
ED_Disclaimer: A/74/267–S/2019/622. The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/74/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
